      <title>美元坚挺，关注个人消费支出数据，新西兰联储维持利率不变，新西兰元下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-firm-with-eyes-pce-data-kiwi-calm-before-rbnz-decision-2024-02-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美元保持稳定，因为交易员隔夜忽略了制成品数据，并等待美联储首选的通胀指标，以寻找美联储何时可能开始降息的线索。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-firm-with-eyes-pce-data-kiwi-calm-before-rbnz-decision-2024-02-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 00:16:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
